---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Side Badger - Free Bill Splitting for Humans (and Badgers)">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content fade-up">
        <div class="hero-badge">
          <span class="badge-dot"></span>
          100% Free Forever
        </div>

        <h1>
          Split bills like a
          <span class="gradient-text">cosmic badger</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="hero-subtitle">
          The totally free, no-tracking, no-ads expense splitter that's suspiciously good.
          We don't want your data. We don't want your money.
          We just want you to split bills with your friends without crying.
        </p>

        <div class="hero-actions flex gap-md flex-wrap">
          <a href="https://app.sidebadger.com" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-confetti" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            Launch the Badger
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M5 12h14"></path>
              <path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="/pricing" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">
            See Pricing (it's free)
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-trust flex items-center gap-lg">
          <div class="trust-item">
            <strong>$0</strong>
            <span>Forever</span>
          </div>
          <div class="trust-divider"></div>
          <div class="trust-item">
            <strong>0</strong>
            <span>Trackers</span>
          </div>
          <div class="trust-divider"></div>
          <div class="trust-item">
            <strong>0</strong>
            <span>Ads</span>
          </div>
          <div class="trust-divider"></div>
          <div class="trust-item">
            <strong>1</strong>
            <span>Badger</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-visual fade-up" data-delay="200">
        <div class="hero-image-container glass">
          <!-- Placeholder for badger mascot -->
          <div class="badger-placeholder">
            <span>Your Badger Here</span>
            <p>Drop your mascot into /public/images/</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Features Section -->
  <section class="features">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header text-center fade-up">
        <h2>Why Side Badger?</h2>
        <p>Because splitting bills shouldn't require a PhD in mathematics or selling your soul to big tech.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bento-grid-lg">
        <div class="feature-card glass fade-up">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M12 2v20M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Actually Free</h3>
          <p>Not "free trial" free. Not "freemium" free. Actually, genuinely, no-strings-attached FREE. We're not hiding premium features behind a paywall because there is no paywall.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card glass fade-up" data-delay="100">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10"/>
              <path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Privacy First</h3>
          <p>Zero trackers. Zero analytics. Zero "we may share with partners." Your expense data stays YOUR expense data. We literally couldn't sell it even if we wanted to (we don't want to).</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card glass fade-up" data-delay="200">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
              <path d="M8 14s1.5 2 4 2 4-2 4-2"/>
              <line x1="9" x2="9.01" y1="9" y2="9"/>
              <line x1="15" x2="15.01" y1="9" y2="9"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>No Ads. Ever.</h3>
          <p>You know what's worse than splitting a $47.23 dinner bill five ways? Doing it while being bombarded with ads for meal kit subscriptions. Never gonna happen here.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card glass fade-up" data-delay="300">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
              <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
              <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/>
              <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Group Friendly</h3>
          <p>Split bills with your roommates, your travel buddies, your D&D party, or that one friend who always "forgets" their wallet. We don't judge.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card glass fade-up" data-delay="400">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect width="18" height="11" x="3" y="11" rx="2" ry="2"/>
              <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Open & Honest</h3>
          <p>Side Badger is a demonstration of what white-label expense splitting can look like. No hidden agenda. Just good vibes and transparent intentions.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card glass fade-up" data-delay="500">
          <div class="feature-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="m12 3-1.912 5.813a2 2 0 0 1-1.275 1.275L3 12l5.813 1.912a2 2 0 0 1 1.275 1.275L12 21l1.912-5.813a2 2 0 0 1 1.275-1.275L21 12l-5.813-1.912a2 2 0 0 1-1.275-1.275L12 3Z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Slightly Silly</h3>
          <p>Because life's too short for boring software. We put a badger in a bill splitter. You're welcome.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-card glass fade-up">
        <h2>Ready to split some bills?</h2>
        <p>Join the badger revolution. It's free, it's private, and it's slightly chaotic in the best way.</p>
        <a href="https://app.sidebadger.com" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-confetti" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          Launch Side Badger
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M5 12h14"></path>
            <path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script>
    // Import and initialize confetti
    import confetti from 'canvas-confetti';

    // Confetti on CTA button clicks
    document.querySelectorAll('.btn-confetti').forEach(btn => {
      btn.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
        const rect = (e.target as HTMLElement).getBoundingClientRect();
        const x = (rect.left + rect.width / 2) / window.innerWidth;
        const y = (rect.top + rect.height / 2) / window.innerHeight;

        confetti({
          particleCount: 100,
          spread: 70,
          origin: { x, y },
          colors: ['#8b5cf6', '#22d3ee', '#ec4899', '#34d399'],
          disableForReducedMotion: true
        });
      });
    });

    // Random celebration (1 in 20 chance on page load)
    if (Math.random() < 0.05) {
      setTimeout(() => {
        confetti({
          particleCount: 50,
          spread: 100,
          origin: { y: 0.6 },
          colors: ['#8b5cf6', '#22d3ee', '#ec4899'],
          disableForReducedMotion: true
        });
      }, 2000);
    }
  </script>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    padding: var(--space-4xl) 0;
  }

  .hero .container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-3xl);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    padding: var(--space-xs) var(--space-md);
    background: rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.3);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--accent-success);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .badge-dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background: var(--accent-success);
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
    50% { opacity: 0.5; transform: scale(1.2); }
  }

  .hero h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    max-width: 550px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .hero-actions {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .hero-trust {
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--glass-bg);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
  }

  .trust-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .trust-item strong {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    color: var(--accent-secondary);
  }

  .trust-item span {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .trust-divider {
    width: 1px;
    height: 40px;
    background: var(--glass-border);
  }

  .hero-visual {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .hero-image-container {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 450px;
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .badger-placeholder {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .badger-placeholder span {
    display: block;
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .badger-placeholder p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
  }

  /* Features */
  .features {
    padding: var(--space-4xl) 0;
  }

  .section-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .section-header p {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .feature-card {
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    transition: transform var(--transition-base), box-shadow var(--transition-base);
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-glow-sm);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-primary), var(--accent-tertiary));
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    color: white;
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .feature-card p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* CTA Section */
  .cta-section {
    padding: var(--space-4xl) 0;
  }

  .cta-card {
    padding: var(--space-3xl);
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cta-card h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .cta-card p {
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-xl);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero .container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      margin: 0 auto var(--space-xl);
    }

    .hero-actions {
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .hero-trust {
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .hero-visual {
      order: -1;
    }

    .hero-image-container {
      max-width: 300px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .hero-trust {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--space-md);
    }

    .trust-divider {
      width: 40px;
      height: 1px;
    }
  }
</style>
